nt-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-100172c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"100172c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-3d6d5cf3-5025-4ef8-bbae-5e159a314db1\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-d7459bc9-6711-4c7f-86d2-1470daf89691\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-0da94f98-d78f-4304-ad24-b67da943c821\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-c030191e-56be-41f0-881e-c4f1d29a61e0\">A palavra &#8220;apology&#8221; em ingl\u00eas \u00e9 usada para se referir a um pedido de desculpas ou a um reconhecimento de erro ou ofensa. \u00c9 uma forma de expressar arrependimento e mostrar que voc\u00ea reconhece que fez algo errado.<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-106bcd64-6231-4d44-9211-c7c648c911bf\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-b99b3296-db28-40ca-905f-e49bba37b9c3\">Por exemplo:<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-b99b3296-db28-40ca-905f-e49bba37b9c3\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-b99b3296-db28-40ca-905f-e49bba37b9c3\"><iframe src=\"https:\/\/play.ht\/embed\/?article_url=https:\/\/play.ht\/drafts\/gLn1gnZGXtfNE2vqLxoxZLNDz4p1\/S6IAu8orR&amp;voice=en-US-GuyNeural\" width=\"100%\" height=\"90px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><strong>I want to offer my sincere apologies for my behavior last night.<\/strong><br \/>Quero oferecer minhas sinceras desculpas pelo meu comportamento ontem \u00e0 noite.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-e415990d-1d2d-461b-8c08-b9ea6f020233\">\u00a0<\/div><div data-block-id=\"block-e415990d-1d2d-461b-8c08-b9ea6f020233\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-3d6d5cf3-5025-4ef8-bbae-5e159a314db1\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-d7459bc9-6711-4c7f-86d2-1470daf89691\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-0da94f98-d78f-4304-ad24-b67da943c821\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-0aa56cde-0ca9-4cc8-a131-301b86423771\">Embora &#8220;apology&#8221; se pare\u00e7a com a palavra &#8220;apologia&#8221; em portugu\u00eas, que pode significar justificativa ou defesa de uma ideia, as duas palavras t\u00eam significados diferentes. Isso torna &#8220;apology&#8221; um falso cognato, ou seja, uma palavra que parece similar a uma palavra em outro idioma, mas que tem significado diferente. \u00c9 importante ter cuidado ao usar palavras como essa em uma conversa ou escrita em ingl\u00eas, pois elas podem ser facilmente mal interpretadas se usadas de maneira inadequada.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-f4cd7a68-7642-4a19-9a51-2022919daff5\">\u00a0<\/div><div data-block-id=\"block-f4cd7a68-7642-4a19-9a51-2022919daff5\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-3d6d5cf3-5025-4ef8-bbae-5e159a314db1\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-d7459bc9-6711-4c7f-86d2-1470daf89691\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-0da94f98-d78f-4304-ad24-b67da943c821\"><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-29112696-7669-4c39-b606-ec75325a463a\">Exemplos:<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-3d4d7852-69a7-4a95-a57d-74f1d7e88325\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-b846e6d7-f5a7-495c-a283-977712fc6a80\"><iframe src=\"https:\/\/play.ht\/embed\/?article_url=https:\/\/play.ht\/drafts\/gLn1gnZGXtfNE2vqLxoxZLNDz4p1\/JyTMiw11H&amp;voice=en-US-JennyNeural\" width=\"100%\" height=\"90px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><strong>I owe you an apology for forgetting your birthday.<\/strong><\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-3aa72c4d-42b1-430e-ac98-3bcf01f287ea\">Eu te devo um pedido de desculpas por ter esquecido seu anivers\u00e1rio.<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-e107b8b5-d6dc-42f4-9239-91270ea9d80d\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-c7cef413-e6b7-43a4-8287-009672600b61\"><iframe src=\"https:\/\/play.ht\/embed\/?article_url=https:\/\/play.ht\/drafts\/gLn1gnZGXtfNE2vqLxoxZLNDz4p1\/o3Cy5T34J&amp;voice=en-US-GuyNeural\" width=\"100%\" height=\"90px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><strong>The company issued a formal apology for the delay in delivering the product.<\/strong><\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-5fae9951-fb4a-48b9-b3ac-f2eb87a097a2\">A empresa emitiu um pedido de desculpas formal pelo atraso na entrega do produto.<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-1a528d27-7f78-42a2-9c2b-113b144cfe87\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-4fd2bb76-3869-4a56-8245-2f5090760cde\"><iframe src=\"https:\/\/play.ht\/embed\/?article_url=https:\/\/play.ht\/drafts\/gLn1gnZGXtfNE2vqLxoxZLNDz4p1\/DDmVJJWFu&amp;voice=en-US-JennyNeural\" width=\"100%\" height=\"90px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><strong>He made an apology to his fans for canceling the concert.<\/strong><\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-bb6f769e-6c14-4484-b7a8-e00376b0d580\">Ele fez um pedido de desculpas aos seus f\u00e3s por cancelar o show.<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-a3ebf530-a36b-438f-8559-0beb37de1b60\">\u00a0<\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-ab5deb0d-7fdd-4d15-ab29-4caf97930987\"><iframe src=\"https:\/\/play.ht\/embed\/?article_url=https:\/\/play.ht\/drafts\/gLn1gnZGXtfNE2vqLxoxZLNDz4p1\/qvaFDEQKd&amp;voice=en-US-GuyNeural\" width=\"100%\" height=\"90px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><strong>She wrote a heartfelt apology letter to her friend after their argument.<\/strong><\/div><div class=\"ql-block\" data-block-id=\"block-316cc4d9-f8de-4ca9-9cf8-81a6ecc13ced\">Ela escreveu uma carta de desculpas sincera para sua amiga depois da discuss\u00e3o.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-130252ed\" data-id=\"130252ed\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6bbad77e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6bbad77e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Siga-nos em<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48a5b59c elementor-shape-rounded elementor-grid-0 e-grid-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-social-icons\" data-id=\"48a5b59c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"social-icons.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-social-icons-wrapper elementor-grid\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-grid-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-icon elementor-social-icon elementor-social-icon-instagram elementor-repeater-item-7ed8adf\" href=\"http:\/\/instagram.com\/gustavodenoronha\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-screen-only\">Instagram<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-grid-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-icon elementor-social-icon elementor-social-icon-telegram elementor-repeater-item-6cfc7f4\" href=\"https:\/\/t.me\/gustavodenoronha\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elem